<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <head>
      <title><%= title %></title>
      <!--    bootstrap-->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
      <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
      <!-- google font -->
      <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Playfair+Display" rel="stylesheet">
   </head>
   <body>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
         <div class="container-fluid backnav">
            <div class="navbar-header">
               <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#myNavbar">
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
               </button>
               <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"> <img src="images/beez.jpg" alt="" width="40px" height="39px"> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="myNavbar">
               <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                  <li><a href="/new">New Post</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/posts">Archive</a></li>
                  <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
               </ul>
               <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                  <li><a href="/login"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-log-in"></span> Login</a></li>
               </ul>
            </div>
         </div>
      </nav>
      <div class="jumbotron">
         <h1 class="text-center">Bezbee Photography</h1>
         <p class="text-center">There is something about the way a picture can capture a moment forever that gives me an adrenaline rush. I have found myself loving photography for many years and the love has continued to grow as I have found myself exploring new places more frequently. There is something refreshing about going back and looking at my camera roll to see all the good memories I've shared with people or sometimes even memories I made by myself. There is an even greater love when it comes to capturing memories for other people.</p>
         <h4 class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" role="button">Learn more</a></h4>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid post">
        <% if (posts) { %>
      	<% for(var i=0; i<3; i++) {%>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      	  <div class="card">
      		<img class="card-img-top" src="<%=posts[i].image %>"  alt="Card image cap" width="100%" height="300px">
      		<div class="card-body">
      		  <h5 class="card-title"><%= posts[i].title %></h5>
      		  <p class="card-text info"> <%= posts[i].content.substring(0, 300) %></p>
            <br>
            <h5 class="card-title text-center"><%= posts[i].author %></h5>
            <h5 class="card-title text-center"> at <%= posts[i].time %> on <%= posts[i].date %> </h5>
      		  <a href="view/<%= posts[i].id %>"> <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" name="button">
      		  Read more</button></a>

      		</div>
      	  </div>
        </div>
      	 <%}%>
      	 <% } else { %>
      		<p>You have no blog posts</p>
      	 <% } %>

      </div>
       </div>
         <div class="photo-gallery">
            <div class="container">
               <div class="intro">
                  <h2 class="text-center">More articles ..</h2>
                  <p class="text-center">
                    Have a look at some of the in depth stories we have looked at over the course of the last six months , from marriage to lifestyle , entertainment and even great expectations . We cover it all .
                  </p>
               </div>
               <br>
               <div class="row-photos">
                  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 item">
                     <a href="#">
                     <img  class="img-responsive" src="images/cover.jpg" alt="">
                     </a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 item">
                     <a href="#">
                     <img class="img-responsive" src="images/wedding2.jpg" alt="">
                     </a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 item">
                     <a href="#">
                     <img class="img-responsive" src="images/lifestyle1.jpg" alt="">
                     </a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-6 item">
                     <a href="#">
                     <img class="img-responsive" src="images/popthree.jpg" alt="">
                     </a>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <br>
         <br>
         <footer class="container-fluid bg-4 text-center ft">
            <p>Created by Zaida Bibi Armien | <a href="#">2018</a></p>
         </footer>
      </div>
      <script>
         function deleteBlog() {
         var r = confirm("Are you sure you want to delete this blog?");
         if (r == true) {
            window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000/delete/<%= posts.id%>';
         }

         }

      </script>
   </body>
</html>
